article_title: The war is not over yet, Netanyahu says.
sentence: Addressing  people  in  Gaza,  Netanyahu  says  "Sinwar  destroyed  your  lives"  and  that  now  that  he  is  dead  “Hamas  will  no  longer  control"  the  territory,  describing  this  as  as  an  opportunity  for  them  to  free  themselves  "from  its  tyranny"  “The  return  of  our  hostages  is  an  opportunity  to  achieve  all  our  goals  and  brings  us  closer  to  the  end  of  the  war,”  he  says.
